  <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4">
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
        <%= render inline: Rails.root.join('public/speedometer.svg').read %>
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4">Distance management</h3>
        <p>Effortless automatic distance and time calculations between patients or customers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
        <%= render inline: Rails.root.join('public/safe.svg').read %>
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4">Safe by design</h3>
        <p>Your data is securely encrypted and meticulously protected.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
        <%= render inline: Rails.root.join('public/magic.svg').read %>
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4">Clutter-free design</h3>
        <p>Intuitive and user-friendly interface for a pleasing experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
        <%= render inline: Rails.root.join('public/peace.svg').read %>
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4">Peace of mind</h3>
        <p>Simplify your routines as you navigate your daily tasks.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
        <%= render inline: Rails.root.join('public/person-bounding-box.svg').read %>
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4">Patient tracker</h3>
        <p>Experience the ease of a multi-platform solution, designed with you in mind, and elevate your efficiency to new heights.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
        <%= render inline: Rails.root.join('public/phone.svg').read %>
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4">Mobile-first approach</h3>
        <p>Your phone is a primary tool at work, so Calcometer is designed to be mobile first and friendly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="d-grid d-sm-flex d-md-flex justify-content-sm-center d-lg-none gap-2 mb-5">
  <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4" href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" role="button">Sign Up</a>
</div>
